headline: Xcel Energy (XEL) Misses Q4 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Xcel (XEL) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -1.37% and -4.44%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
